This paper discusses the upcoming standards in wireless local area networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication technologies. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper also discusses the technical issues and functionality of the wireless broadband technology, which can be related to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also mentions the problems with the current standing IEEE 802.11, which can be related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.COM (Computer Communications and Networks).
